data.description:
Discover the perfect blend of modern luxury and comfort in this meticulously crafted townhome located in a convenient and amenity-rich neighborhood. Boasting 2 bedrooms downstairs and an additional loft space upstairs, this residence offers a versatile layout that adapts to your lifestyle. Step inside and be greeted by the timeless elegance of tile and hardwood flooring that seamlessly traverse the entire home. Upgraded kitchen features solid surface counters, stainless steel appliances, and LOTS of cabinet space. Both bathrooms have also been upgraded to provide a  modern look. 
Marvel at the high ceilings that grace the living spaces, creating an open and airy atmosphere flooded with natural light. The loft space, a hidden gem, provides the perfect canvas for a home office, cozy reading nook, or even an extra guest room. Venture outside to your private fenced backyard, a tranquil retreat that includes a screened patio, offering the ideal setting for al fresco dining, morning coffee, or simply unwinding after a busy day. Convenience is at your doorstep, with amenities galore in the neighborhood and easy access to nearby attractions. This townhome is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle upgrade. The home owners current loan is assumable for VA buyers (3.875% interest rate) Schedule a showing today!
